    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661330/extras/5527c63719e61499d88d87fe2502570a.poster.avif?t=1770884450\" width=780 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661330/extras/5527c63719e61499d88d87fe2502570a.webm?t=1770884450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661330/extras/5527c63719e61499d88d87fe2502570a.mp4?t=1770884450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><i>《SacriFire》</i></strong>是一款即将面市的<strong>RPG</strong>游戏，灵感源自让开发团队成员们爱上电玩的90年代传奇RPG作品。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>激烈战斗</strong>：融合了实时与回合制战斗的独特系统，实现了既充满挑战又淋漓畅快的战斗体验。与同伴并肩作战，选择种类丰富的武器，叠加多种攻击形成复杂的组合技。<br></li><li><strong>精美画面</strong>：同时使用像素与3D图形，既有怀旧游戏的风格，又不失创新数码特效的精湛。手绘的动画角色与3D建模的环境完美融合。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661330/extras/bd5b5a9d98745f6e2a4b30d54e184c10.poster.avif?t=1770884450\" width=780 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661330/extras/bd5b5a9d98745f6e2a4b30d54e184c10.webm?t=1770884450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661330/extras/bd5b5a9d98745f6e2a4b30d54e184c10.mp4?t=1770884450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>道德深度</strong>：《SacriFire》的原创故事在继承经典RPG模式的同时又有所颠覆。多位角色的设定会让你感到熟悉，但却又不知接下来会发生什么！ <br></li><li><strong>两个世界</strong>：游历庞大的地下城Antioch和田园诗歌般的灵性之地Erebus，丰富完善的游戏世界同时包括了奇幻与科幻元素。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661330/extras/5f5eb45546f5ecc88c03e358954cc342.poster.avif?t=1770884450\" width=780 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661330/extras/5f5eb45546f5ecc88c03e358954cc342.webm?t=1770884450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661330/extras/5f5eb45546f5ecc88c03e358954cc342.mp4?t=1770884450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>精深的游戏机制</strong>：选择不同的战斗风格，锻造武器，解开谜题，探索奥妙的地城。<br></li><li><strong>原创音乐与专业配音</strong>：由G4F及传奇作曲家<strong>樱庭统</strong>创作的原声音轨。Sound Cadence Studios的专业团队让《SacriFire》的角色更加栩栩如生！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661330/extras/7612e4fad10124c716bccd19f1b71a8a.webp?t=1770884450\" width=323 height=48 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661330/extras/7781f5902aff79cc2ad9a1a7aa2ad682.avif?t=1770884450\" width=610 height=110 /></span><br>Co-financed by Ministry of Culture and National Heritage",
